Product description

Being chic doesn't always mean your accessories have to be flashy and loud. Maybe a subtle flair and unique qualities is exactly what you're looking for. If that's the case, then we're confident you will like this Fossil Grant watch. It's the perfect combination of smooth, fashionable, and exquisite. Don't get us wrong, you will no doubt turn heads with this beauty on your wrist, but in a manner that is more like a quiet beckoning than an obvious solicitation for attention. It features a sleek blue leather band, which is perfectly paired with a rose-gold 44mm stainless steel case. The combination of these two aspects work in splendid harmony as the case creates a glossy look and the band keeps it grounded with its simplicity. The best part about this watch is its dial, which flaunts a creative blue pattern. This is where that subtle flair comes in ladies! The pattern is just enough to make a fashionable statement, but without making it seem like you're trying. Another aspect that contributes to the glamour of this Fossil watch is its rose-gold detail, which creates a beautifully polished contrast with the design that's on the dial. This time-keeper is a winner, hands down, but it's not all good looks. This watch can handle up to 50 meters / 165 feet / 5 atm of water, so water damage is not in the books. In addition to its water resistance, its casing is made out of stainless steel, and its face is guarded by a heavy-duty mineral crystal. This watch can stand up to some serious roughhousing, without question. So if you're a lady who loves to stay in vogue but doesn't care to put on a show, this is your watch. Not only will you be killing it in the fashion world, but it'll last you a long time.
